 am able to run.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my way\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"my name\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was almost more of a relief to make the team this time.\\\"\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a relief\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cockrell is an advocate for the mental health of student-athletes, which she addressed in her commencement speech at USC.\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1154, \"end\": 1157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USC_Trojans\", \"score\": 0.9999999930173544, \"rank\": 6.420839156505612e-09, \"text\": \"USC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USC_Trojans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USC_Trojans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cockrell\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"an advocate\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"the mental health\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"student-athletes\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"her commencement speech\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe two things I do not like to talk about are the fact that I have battled depression on and off since my 10th-grade year and that I am a perfectionist,\\\" Cockrell said.\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two things\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"depression\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"my 10th-grade year\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"a perfectionist\", \"from\